    <published>2020-06-14T05:40:39.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-06-14T10:29:44.165Z</updated>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;描述&lt;br&gt;阿克曼(Ackmann)函数A(m，n)中，m，n定义域是非负整数(m≤3,n≤10)，函数值定义为：&lt;br&gt;   akm(m,n) = n+1;         (m=0时)&lt;br&gt;   akm(m,n) = akm(m-1,1);  (m&amp;gt;0,n=0时)&lt;br&gt;   akm(m,n) = akm(m-1,akm(m, n-1)); （m,n&amp;gt;0时)&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
